{"tid":1816294,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[721警黑合作翻版]好想幫梨木樹手足重建連儂牆","createTime":"2020-01-08T06:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T03:33:47.000Z","uid":138667,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"58e48bc6137f6219ca6c4ffdda46747fcff820c1","tid":1816294,"uid":138667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:51:44.000Z","msg":"修例風波：逾40人梨木樹清連儂牆險爆衝突<br />\n01月08日(三) 06:33更新 03:48建立<br />\n<br />\n今日(8日)凌晨零時許，大約40多名男女步至葵涌梨木樹邨巴士總站，帶同漆鏟及掃帚等工具，清理巴士總站內連儂牆，期間有街坊見狀不滿，上前喝止，遭到撕紙及拆連儂牆的男女指罵；疑有人罵至面紅耳赤之際，手持木棍、掃帚、伸縮棍向對方追打及用墨潑向對方。<br />\n現場消息指，多輛警車載同數十名防暴警員到場戒備及了解。警方調查後，沒有發現武器及傷者，事件中無人被捕，警方列作糾紛處理。直至在場人士將牆上紙張撕去及清理妥當後，由警員護送在場人士截乘的士離去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iaHEf4s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiaHEf4s.png&h=c546c84d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/89Kjf4t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F89Kjf4t.png&h=44f4a642&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qoX1upv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqoX1upv.png&h=2faf4cae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VKGQ7bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVKGQ7bc.png&h=f6bbd945&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4r4rFwd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4r4rFwd.png&h=a2572f55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">根本就係721</span></span><br />\n黑警護送黑社會走<br />\n又話見唔到有武器屌你<br />\n睇到眼火爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有無手足11號一定去梨木樹幫佢哋重建連儂牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n佢哋隻連豬連狗整得咁靚<br />\n比班黑社會整爛曬一定好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊去幫佢哋手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />山卡啦地方由佢啦"},{"pid":"4ccfb1ea98dca20c8934dab2ccb4edbbc35a87ce","tid":1816294,"uid":138667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:55:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mw5Zf73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMw5Zf73.jpg&h=ef0a00a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n變咗咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062d81b89133f7fb7684e1caf0f742f0ddacf7c3","tid":1816294,"uid":10626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:55:50.000Z","msg":"111重建"},{"pid":"4bccd10af654d27d85c3244d112e31056ccaa63d","tid":1816294,"uid":138667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:56:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xXVFK1D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxXVFK1D.jpg&h=c07d3526&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全部爛晒"},{"pid":"d388819a30b034da07571149b1d2055d889ae411","tid":1816294,"uid":138667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:56:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7qXs9tv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7qXs9tv.jpg&h=f2e64491&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又見唔到武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ecc75f56d95d9da4ec33f684973a254fb8be98f","tid":1816294,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:58:46.000Z","msg":"班藍屍仲要話連儂牆搞到社區烏煙瘴氣，睇到咩人先係製造垃圾未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e096481941ca3788dc96a2f5437982fa40b9348e","tid":1816294,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58e48bc6137f6219ca6c4ffdda46747fcff820c1","tid":1816294,"uid":138667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:51:44.000Z","msg":"修例風