n每區區議會需在該區人流就多既位置，<strong>安裝正式既連農文宣牆 (情況有如廣告箱)，</strong> <br />\n同時安排保安公司管理。 費用就香港人既錢(公帑)支付。<br />\n<br />\n以上工程，由黃色工程公司負責，當中可請手足full / part time幫手。<br />\n對家用呢重方法玩咗廿幾年，今次到香港人！<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>[不同政見，都可以提交文宣]</strong></ins><br />\n機會平等，所有人都可以將文宣交到當區區議員手上<br />\n佢地會有既定「機制」去分類放上連農<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>我地要好好理用手上 區議會權力同資源</ins></strong><br />\n- 18-1區文宣正式化<br />\n- 擴大及鞏固黃色經濟圈<br />\n- 支援手足 保護手足<br />\n<br />\n「18區議會入」港共自己都係行人隧道做文宣 我地點解唔可以？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1813044\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1813044</a>"},{"pid":"4bbdaa81edea677b88ac817dd62e08c0afe4a6d0","tid":1816294,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:04:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6dd758d545c0f09df842faf14063693ef9ca89f","tid":1816294,"uid":138667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:33:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8505c977b4d37e7cb37772211496d101803cb26","tid":1816294,"uid":138667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:34:11.000Z","msg":"一方有難 百方支援<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329aa261aefc37dedda2e1408ac546533ca1530d","tid":1816294,"uid":138667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:34:27.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a29359cb7d56b0357a5d0753ede7baacf31f5a5","tid":1816294,"uid":138667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:34:51.000Z","msg":"梨木樹手足我哋黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48ac3528ac6776a41c55825cc5eb64452f9fcce","tid":1816294,"uid":138667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:35:11.000Z","msg":"一齊入去幫拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46945ea8e706b6b3db8ada92de0e687cdcdf96d6","tid":1816294,"uid":112